FBIS4-14774 "drsov064_p_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-064 Daily Report 1 Apr 1994 CAUCASUS Armenia President Reaffirms Settlement Desire President Reaffirms Settlement Desire LD0104215694 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1550 GMT 1 Apr 94 LD0104215694 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Russian BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondents Tigran Liloyan and Sergey Ostanin] [Text] Yerevan, 1 Apr -- Levon Ter-Petrosyan, the president of Armenia, reaffirmed his country's desire to assist in a constructive solution to the Karabakh conflict at a meeting today with a delegation from the CIS Interparliamentary Assembly. He described the Commonwealth parliamentarians' efforts as serious, responsible, and also noble. "In Armenia you will only encounter the desire to make your work easier", L. Ter-Petrosyan stressed.
